definitions.definition: A suburban area and prison in north-west Newport , Isle of Wight , England ( OS grid ref SZ4990 ) .
A northern suburb of Johannesburg , Gauteng province, South Africa .
A suburb of Rockhampton , Rockhampton Region, Queensland , Australia .
